commit c5d6acdc4c9c82c6eff6ba21465a5f153bec378b
Author: Sebastian Utz <su@rtme.net>
Date:   Mon Mar 31 13:46:19 2025 +0200

    Fix new column collection to not contain duplicates
    
    Duplicated new columns weren't a real issue besides memory consumption
    until the field limit detection on dynamically added columns was fixed
    by https://github.com/crate/crate/commit/ea6fa68af2.
    
    Fixes #17691.
    
    (cherry picked from commit 2aa7e269ec7bc92d6f4dfa68392f6293905861d7)

